{"tid":1432894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者們多謝你地，但你哋需要團結！","createTime":"2019-08-08T10:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:51:56.000Z","uid":117622,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"55770febec41307086e74a00beaeaba149a32bc7","tid":1432894,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"依家日日都有警方記者招待會<br />\n記者好努力去問每個問題<br />\n但係警方亦都有佢嘅語言藝術<br />\n兜圈兜圈兜圈兜圈<br />\n仲有個爛鬼MC喺度嘈喧巴閉<br />\n有幾個建議比記者你地參考吓<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">(小弟辯論技巧，只有小學雞程度，屌得細力啲。)</span><br />\n<br />\n1.團結一致，充足預備計劃！<br />\n2.每間報館記者都要開過TG group！<br />\n3.每一日都要定立至少一個重點問題。<br />\n4.重點問題要假設警方答案。<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">(其實唔難，佢日日都係講同一個答案。)</span><br />\n5.追問就算係第二間報館都要追問第一個重點問題，逼到佢入牆角。<br />\n<br />\n假設<br />\n1.重點問題<br />\n發現警方使用過期催淚彈，警方如何釋除公眾疑慮？<br />\n2.假設答案<br />\n警方使用任何武力都會有適當嘅指引，公眾係可以放心，如果有任何問題，都可以向投訴警察科投訴，我哋會有既定程序去處理。<br />\n3.追問<span style=\"color: red;\">(準備封閉式問題不問開放式問題)</span><br />\n-警方使用過期催淚彈有沒有指引？❌<br />\n-請講解警方使用過期催淚彈指引？✅<br />\n<br />\n-警方指引有沒有處理過期催淚彈守則？❌<br />\n-請講解警方指引係如何處理過期催淚彈？✅<br />\n<br />\n-使用過期催淚彈有沒有副作用和後遺症？❌<br />\n-請解釋使用過期催淚彈後副作用和後遺症。✅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只有一個問題</span><br />\n唔好俾機會佢兜圈或者唔答，反正你問佢咁多問題都好似冇答一樣，如果有一個問題問正死穴，好過你問1000個問題。<br />\n另外記者我相信你都真係有好多問題想問。<br />\n記住我哋<span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆</span>團結一致！<br />\n犧牲小我完成大我！彰顯香港人智慧！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"54bc12a8926b185c69a3b5946e34e45df722e7e9","tid":1432894,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209c3f3f4d8feb3a203c1642ac6f3d746651555a","tid":1432894,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d3f5d284270499a8098a5c7feeb8ac5d43d569","tid":1432894,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f93195450204a473b410c35f9ef18b6eb011c06","tid":1432894,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d48315bcb93b15b0a25070c88caa426d550d1523","tid":1432894,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20dd423f9a88866f5d2ac7e53a4f2a0cc366ded0","tid":1432894,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861ec171cc5a2999c3e6fed13e789ede0b9c0e97","tid":1432894,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c02ebb2f1815f72988404539751a203d968bf2","tid":1432894,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"佢哋行家一定有溝通<br />\n駛唔駛你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b348b9375acbc47f6541aac63ace2b0d9dfac418","tid":1432894,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cf8600970b1211dd4c51ee1774387fd01510ee","tid":1432894,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"開波TVb<br />\n解圍就星島<br />\n埋尾南早<br />\n<br />\n吊你喇"},{"pid":"deb7c57b2ec24e89d78f57b766a45df6eb8f397d","tid":1432894,"uid":294858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":